{"tid":1976479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"距離打仗唔係好耐，問心嗰句，有幾多人係練足先發夢？","createTime":"2020-04-17T09:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T12:06:18.000Z","uid":340106,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"629c358fe59451bce2c9b683c26ab3091967051b","tid":1976479,"uid":340106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:20:38.000Z","msg":"耐力、跑速、跳欄、爬牆，一啲基本反擒術，甚至抗打都有同朋友一齊練過下，總之就係練埋武術。<br />\n<br />\n利申我自己本身係和理非，但我哋都已經意識到和理非唔等於大唒，係好吟沉，唔期望你有能力打狗救人，但至少唔哂其他手足唔需要救你而你可以自救先。嚟緊剩返唔算多亦唔算少嘅時間，係足夠練哂上面嘅嘢，當然未必可以學到好精啦。<br />\n<br />\n係，冇錯，黑警係繼續會殺人，但我唔想見到弱質纖纖/肚腩大過屎忽嘅手足橫屍街頭，憎黑警嘅同時唔好忘記強化自己。輕鬆跳過路邊鐵欄、爬過約兩米半嘅牆，自問過得去，嚟緊都會繼續練上面講嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7ef7c320803a5eb05eeef9636cd154d8b30dece2","tid":1976479,"uid":340106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:24:28.000Z","msg":"做過前線、獨居兼無親無故嘅必然係被殺首選，你哋係走唔甩，一定要練"},{"pid":"245c0bdf42eb127bd363e41e287a13266612c398","tid":1976479,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576f90b86a2b14ec715dd9f4ee87e5aa56fac1a0","tid":1976479,"uid":340106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:37:57.000Z","msg":"幫推唔該，p牌好慘"},{"pid":"f8a09be008d41b3a278165d9be198c94bcb849f5","tid":1976479,"uid":312238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:41:49.000Z","msg":"為身體定咩都好，練好啲體能都係好"},{"pid":"382e72721e5b42a0ab424f7759966605e149f2fd","tid":1976479,"uid":90377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"有冇港島巴打團練<img src=\"/assets/faces/no